last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 1
last_episode_to_air.overview: This powerful documentary about the role of Native Americans in contemporary music history-featuring some of the greatest music stars of our time-exposes a critical missing chapter, revealing how indigenous musicians helped shape the soundtracks of our lives and, through their contributions, influenced popular culture.

name: Rumble: The Indians Who Rocked the World
original_name: Rumble: The Indians Who Rocked the World
overview: Documentary about the role of Native Americans in popular music history, a little-known story built around the incredible lives and careers of the some of the greatest music legends.
